---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Transcribr - Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 mt-10">
    <header class="mb-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-800 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">for Transcribr</p>
    </header>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Last updated: September 2, 2025</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        This Privacy Policy describes how Transcribr ("we," "our," or "us")
        collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our mobile
        application and website, <a
          href="https://transcribr.org"
          class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">https://transcribr.org</a
        > (the "Service"). By using the Service, you agree to the collection and
        use of your information in accordance with this policy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        Information We Collect
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We collect several types of information to provide and improve our
        Service:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
        <li>
          <strong>Personal Information:</strong> When you create an account, we may
          collect personal details such as your name and email address. If you sign
          up using social authentication (e.g., Google, Apple), we collect the information
          permitted by your social media provider.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Audio Files and Transcripts:</strong> To perform our core Service,
          you upload audio files (MP3, MP4) and we generate text transcripts. These
          files and the resulting transcripts are stored securely to allow you to
          manage them.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Usage Data:</strong> We automatically collect information about
          how you use the Service, including the number of transcriptions created,
          total minutes transcribed, and your subscription/purchase history.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        How We Use Your Information
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">The information we collect is used to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4 mt-4">
        <li>Provide, operate, and maintain our Service.</li>
        <li>Process and manage your transcriptions.</li>
        <li>Improve and personalize your user experience.</li>
        <li>Understand and analyze how you use our Service.</li>
        <li>
          Communicate with you, including for customer support and product
          updates.
        </li>
        <li>
          Process payments and manage your subscriptions or one-time purchases.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We take the security of your data seriously. As outlined in our Product
        Requirements Document, user data, including personal details, uploaded
        audio files, and generated transcripts, are encrypted at rest and in
        transit. We implement robust authentication and authorization mechanisms
        to protect your account and data privacy.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
        While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your
        information, no method of transmission over the Internet or method of
        electronic storage is 100% secure.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        Third-Party Services
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We use the following third-party services to help us operate our
        business:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
        <li>
          <strong>RevenueCat:</strong> We use RevenueCat to process and manage your
          subscriptions and one-time purchases. All payment information is handled
          securely by RevenueCat, and we do not store your payment details.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cloud Storage Provider:</strong> We use a cloud storage provider
          (e.g., AWS S3, Google Cloud Storage) to securely store your uploaded audio
          files and generated transcripts.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Depending on your location, you may have rights under data privacy
        regulations such as GDPR or CCPA. These rights may include:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4 mt-4">
        <li>The right to access your personal data.</li>
        <li>The right to rectify inaccurate data.</li>
        <li>The right to request deletion of your data.</li>
        <li>The right to object to the processing of your data.</li>
        <li>The right to delete your personal data.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
        To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <a
          href="mailto:support@transcribr.org"
          class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@transcribr.org</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        Changes to This Privacy Policy
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you
        of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. We
        encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any
        changes.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4 mt-4">
        <li>
          By email: <a
            href="mailto:support@transcribr.org"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@transcribr.org</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          By visiting this page on our website: <a
            href="https://transcribr.org/contact"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
            >https://transcribr.org/contact</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
